latestPosts.caption:
Finally uploading the video from our 5-day cluster visit. An experience we’ll truly never forget, especially with the best teammates by my side! The fun we had, the memories we made, and everything we learned along the way will always stay with us. From all the hard work we put in, to connecting with the artisans and getting to know them and their craft so closely it was something really special.🥹

The effort behind this project was real, and we’re proud to finally share it.
Hope you enjoy the video as much as we enjoyed living every moment of it! 💙✨

Shot & edited by- @priyanka.jaiswalll 
Voiceover by- @akshatgyan1 Thank you for the amazing voiceover and for being such a big help! 🙌
